title: Democratic Debate Preview
itunes:title: Democratic Debate Preview
description:
Kevin spoke with Kevin Walling, Democratic Strategist at HG Creative Media, and Jack Kingston, Former Georgia Congressman and Trump 2020 campaign surrogate. They previewed tomorrow's democratic presidential debate, comments from Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin on trade, Fiona Hill getting subpoenaed, and the Biden family.
